animeTitle: Rudolf to Ippaiattena x Godzilla x Toho Cinemas Moving Logo Eizou
animeDescription: A collaboration promoting the Rudolf to Ippaiattena film, wherein the movie's two main characters encounter the Toho logo and Godzilla. It was aired in Toho theaters across Japan.
animeRelated: ['Rudolf to Ippaiattena', 'Toho Cinemas x Pokemon Go']
